Package: plotme
Title: Plot Me
Description: plotme is designed to plot "Open", "High", and "Low" stock prices 
  from stock datasets. The package takes a `.csv` file as input, processes the 
  data, and outputs an insightful and interactive plot to visualize stock price 
  movements over time. This helps users easily analyze trends and patterns in 
  stock data.
Version: 1.0
